## Quick Reference

| Step | Required? | Where |
|------|-----------|-------|
| Search existing components | ✅ Always | `client/components/ui/` + `client/components/walmart/` |
| Named export (no default) | ✅ Always | Component `.tsx` |
| CSS module with semantic tokens | ✅ Always | Component `.module.css` |
| Responsive breakpoints | ✅ If layout | CSS module |
| `prefers-reduced-motion` | ✅ If animated | CSS module |
| Component Library page | ✅ Always | `client/pages/component-library/` |
| Route + sidebar + i18n | ✅ Always | `App.tsx` + `ComponentLibraryLayout.tsx` + locales |
| ComponentTester sandbox | ✅ If interactive | `ComponentTester.tsx` |
| Theme compliance check | ✅ Always | Run grep commands |

---

## Enforcement Level

**CRITICAL** — Every new component must follow this process. Code reviews MUST reject components that skip the post-creation checklist.
